oil until an adequate, permanent cover is established. This requirement may be suspended if the operator demonstrates to the department's satisfaction that it is not needed to control air or water pollution and erosion.</p><p><strong>Final Deficiency:</strong> This is the final deficiency (Bobs version) for this rule.</p></div></td></tr>
